    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited for whoever gets to drive this beauty home. It\u2019s been kept in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
