      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an automotive specimen of exceptional caliber, maintained to the most exacting standards of preservation. This vehicle exhibits a level of refinement synonymous with showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior devoid of any discernable wear. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a high-integrity asset of the highest order.",
