    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total dream. This car is in pristine, showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since the day I got it! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives just as smooth as it looks. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. I'm happy to answer any questions or have you over to take a look. Can't wait to see this beauty go to a great new home!",
      "price": 44500.0,
