    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of Bavarian engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system that remains in peak operational sync. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the chassis has undergone rigorous inspection to confirm zero subframe fatigue, while the suspension retains its original kinematic precision. This vehicle exhibits no fluid seepage and maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders, representing a true collector-grade specimen with unparalleled mechanical integrity.",
